              <li>Restriction Note B: Not open to students who have taken or are taking MATH 122 or MATH 130 or MATH 131, except by permission of the Department of Mathematics and Statistics</li>
              <li>MATH 150 and MATH 151 cover the material of MATH 139, MATH 140, MATH 141, MATH 222 </li>
